[{"author": "赵林波", "body": "【根本原因】：销售日期筛选12月22-12月31号数据，列表第10页和第11页出现重复carId: Sws5cOcvKO
【直接原因】：列表根据carId作为列表重新渲染的key。一样的key导致列表重用出现问题，出现部分数据闪动情况。
[~chenbing01]需要服务端相关同学查看", "created": "2025-01-03T16:33:56.000+0800"}, {"author": " 陈兵·", "body": "第十页：https://trace.souche-inc.com/logTraceidResult.html?tid=1735893302214_NeCy&&mydate=2025-01-03&&from=INDEX&&alarmId=undefined
第十一：https://trace.souche-inc.com/logTraceidResult.html?tid=1735893307338_jNrw&&mydate=2025-01-03&&from=INDEX&&alarmId=undefined", "created": "2025-01-03T16:36:43.000+0800"}, {"author": "fanlongfei", "body": "观察到的现象就是使用nqquery时,观察到多次点击车辆id不断跳动,第10页跳动的id比较多,第11页多次点击也会有id跳动.

第10页ng查询:{ "andQuerys": { "date_delete": "0", "org_id": "Ae6BttYyDf" }, "fetchFields": "id", "filters": [ "shop_code IN [\"03856713\"]" ], "indexName": "crazyracing_kartrider", "key_word": "", "orQuerys": { "business_type": [ "car_default_type" ] }, "querys": "(operation_phase IN [\"5j4qm0tNbC_phase_node_WZgTRtWjBz\"]) AND pay_time>=\"2024-12-22 00:00:00\" AND pay_time<=\"2024-12-31 23:59:59\" AND (operation_phase IN [\"5j4qm0tNbC_phase_node_WZgTRtWjBz\"])", "scroll": false, "scrollTimeout": 0, "size": 10, "sort": { "pay_time": "desc" }, "src": "car", "start": 90 }

第11页ng查询:{ "andQuerys": { "date_delete": "0", "org_id": "Ae6BttYyDf" }, "fetchFields": "id", "filters": [ "shop_code IN [\"03856713\"]" ], "indexName": "crazyracing_kartrider", "key_word": "", "orQuerys": { "business_type": [ "car_default_type" ] }, "querys": "(operation_phase IN [\"5j4qm0tNbC_phase_node_WZgTRtWjBz\"]) AND pay_time>=\"2024-12-22 00:00:00\" AND pay_time<=\"2024-12-31 23:59:59\" AND (operation_phase IN [\"5j4qm0tNbC_phase_node_WZgTRtWjBz\"])", "scroll": false, "scrollTimeout": 0, "size": 10, "sort": { "pay_time": "desc" }, "src": "car", "start": 100 }", "created": "2025-01-03T16:52:54.000+0800"}, {"author": "", "body": "经排查,车辆有很多销售日期相同的数据,在排序时就会产生位置跳动问题,建议车商配合创建时间一起筛选", "created": "2025-01-06T11:16:44.000+0800"}, {"author": "fanlongfei", "body": "经排查,车商有很多销售日期相同的数据,在排序时就会产生位置跳动问题,就会导致页面闪屏,建议车商配合创建时间一起筛选
", "created": "2025-01-06T11:17:33.000+0800"}, {"author": " 陈兵·", "body": "https://f2e-assets.souche-inc.com/projects/data-fe/cybertron-cooperation-web/index.html?tofd=1740649759376#/dashboard/21608
